The late Chief of Staff to President Muhammadu Buhari, Abba Kyari, will be buried on Saturday Personal Assistant on New Media to President Buhari, Basir Ahmad, made this known on his Twitter handle on Saturday morning. He said, “Mallam Abba Kyari will be buried later today in Abuja according to Islamic rites.”v We just received the body of Abba Kyari the deceased Chief of Staff the President in Abuja. In strict observation of the protocol put in place for the burial of Coronavirus victims by the @NCDCgov and the Federal Ministry of Health, the funeral prayer and burial will be private.